I'm going to try to not run
out of time either.

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:25.100
So it's going to
start rotating.

00:07:25.100 --> 00:07:27.930
So the left hand side's going
to go below the page.

00:07:27.930 --> 00:07:29.630
The right hand side's going
to be above the page.

